    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Kageyama Clan, Level 4+<br />You are a little bit more sensitive than most people, you are quite quick to anger. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li>Increase your Intelligence or Wisdom score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li>When you would roll a die as a result of <em><strong>Prelude to Destruction</strong></em> you reroll 1s and 2s, taking the second result.</li><li>Damage you deal while you are in your 100% explosion ignores resistance.</li></ul>",
